pe=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Albi\">ALBI\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marci\">M\u003C/span>·F·OUF\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Pollionis\">POLLIONIS\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>OPER·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Cai\">C\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domiti\">DOMITI\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Cai\">C\u003C/span>·F·VOT·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Rufi\">RUFI\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>ALYPUS·SIMBUL\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>MERCURIO\u003Cbr id=\"al9-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>AUGUSTO\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text: CIL\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 5\">line.5: \u003Cspan>Mommsen oper(a) vel oper(is) opinor\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>[By the order of?] Marcus Albus Pollio, son of Marcus, of [tribe] Oufentina, for the work of Gaius Domitius Rufus, son of Gaius, of [tribe] Voturia, ALYPUS SIMBUL. To Mercury Augustus.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Manganaro suggests 'ex testamento' rather than 'iussu', and notes that the onomastics are Domitianic. SIMBVL is suggested by Mommsen possibly to be a transliteration of συμβολαιογράφος, a suggestion broadly followed by Manganaro.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7224\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 50, 69, 72 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kragelund 2008 120 n.15 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001895\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001895\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[186,189,192,195,198,201,204,207],{"id":187,"html":188},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[iussu?] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marci\">M(arci)\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Albi\">Albi\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3